port)\",\n      \"b2\": \"Enable 2FA (Google Authenticator) on Binance AND SignalX\",\n      \"b3\": \"Disable \\\"Enable Withdrawals\\\" on your Binance API keys\",\n      \"b4\": \"In doubt, revoke the keys on Binance instantly\",\n      \"b5\": \"Your keys are AES-128 encrypted in our database — unreadable even by support\"\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently asked questions\",\n      \"q1\": \"Can the bot lose my money?\",\n      \"a1\": \"Yes, like any trading tool. Stop-loss limits the loss per trade (~3% by default). Start with PAPER to validate the strategy.\",\n      \"q2\": \"How do I cancel my Premium subscription?\",\n      \"a2\": \"Profile → Premium → \\\"Cancel subscription\\\". You keep access until the end of the paid period.\",\n      \"q3\": \"Does the bot trade while I sleep?\",\n      \"a3\": \"Yes, 24/7. The bot scans markets every 5 minutes. You can disable it anytime via the toggle.\",\n      \"q4\": \"Why isn't the bot opening positions?\",\n      \"a4\": \"It's waiting for strong signals (RSI + EMA + Claude AI validation). Patience — a bot that doesn't open is a bot that doesn't lose.\",\n      \"q5\": \"Are my API keys really safe?\",\n      \"a5\": \"Yes. They are AES-128 encrypted before storage. No one — not even support — can read them in clear. Plus, without Withdrawal permission, they can only be used for trading.\"\n    },\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"title\": \"Need help?\",\n      \"text\": \"Drop us a line, we reply within 24 business hours.\"\n    },\n    \"footer\": \"Crypto trading involves risk. Past performance does not guarantee future results.\",\n    \"video\": {\n      \"coming_soon\": \"🎬 Video tutorial coming soon\",\n      \"coming_soon_desc\": \"We're finalizing the edit. Check back soon — it covers everything in 6 minutes.\",\n      \"watch_title\": \"Video tutorial (6 min)\",\n      \"watch_on_youtube\": \"Watch on YouTube\",\n      \"duration_label\": \"Duration: 6 minutes\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"qu